{Speech 6}{}{Me? Well, if you're asking... I'm Jesus. Jesus Mordino. Same as my father. Only he's Big Jesus, the head of the whole Mordino family here in New Reno. So most folks call me Little Jesus. To keep things from getting confused, see?}
{Speech 6 Answer 8}{}{What did you say about the Mordino Family?@@What's this Mordino family you were talking about?}
{Speech 6 Answer 20}{}{I heard about your family. I also heard your boys are a force to be reckoned with.}
{Speech 6 Answer 21}{}{I need work. Doesn't the Mordino family hire people?}
{Speech 6 Answer 17}{}{Do you know where I could go in town to have some fun?}
{Speech 6 Answer 7}{}{I see. I've got a few more questions...}
{Speech 7}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог}
{Speech 7 Answer 34}{}{I'm from Joey in the Den, here to pick up a batch of drugs.}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{What did you say about the Mordino Family?@@What's this Mordino family you were talking about?}
