{Speech 8}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог}
{Speech 8 Answer 20}{}{Sounds like the Mordino family is one of the most worthy families. I'd like to do business with you.}
{Speech 8 Answer 21}{}{I need work. Doesn't the Mordino family hire people?}
{Speech 8 Answer 23}{}{You Mordinos talk big, but you've got few connections. What do you say to that, Little Jesus?}
{Speech 8 Answer 10}{}{And what did you say about Redding?}
{Speech 8 Answer 9}{}{Redding? Where's that?}
{Speech 8 Answer 7}{}{Sounds like the Mordinos have a bright future. I've got a few questions for you...}
{Speech 9}{}{Время:60000 Нет ответа:Завершить диалог}
{Speech 9 Answer 11}{}{And what did you say about Redding?}
{Speech 9 Answer 7}{}{I've got more questions.}
{Speech 9 Answer 12}{}{Is there a crowd of junkies there?}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{I gotta go, Jesus...}
{Speech 10}{}{A bunch of miners, digging in the dirt, but they love to FLY, you know what I mean?}
{Speech 10 Answer 11}{}{Not really. What do you mean?}
{Speech 11}{}{They mine gold, but we give them something much better than gold, see? They hand over ALL their gold just to get even a LITTLE Jet. Everybody's happy.}
{Speech 11 Answer 7}{}{Sounds like it, I've got a few more questions...}
{Speech 12}{}{Okay, the first time they try Jet, they can't handle the craving afterward. You can never use it just once.}
{Speech 12 Answer 13}{}{Where did Jet come from?}
{Speech 12 Answer 7}{}{I understand. Listen, I've got a few more questions...}
{Speech 13}{}{Jet? From here. See, we don't mine gold, we make it: liquid gold. Jet. Lucky for the miners, it costs almost nothing to produce. We ship it to Redding, they get high, they fly, they ship us the gold. It's simple.}
{Speech 13 Answer 14}{}{How long has this been going on? Sounds like you could control all of Northern California if Jet is that powerful.}
{Speech 14}{}{You're right, see, we didn't always have Jet. But we found this guy - he looked at the crap we were selling and said he could make it better. And he did. Now he works for us. It's simple.}
{Speech 14 Answer 15}{}{Who is this guy and where is he?}
{Speech 15}{}{His name is Myron. As for where he is, that's something you don't need to know.}
{Speech 15 Answer 23}{}{Why don't you be a good boy and tell me anyway?}
{Speech 15 Answer 7}{}{I see. I've got a few more questions...}
{Speech 16}{}{His name is Myron. We keep him at the stables, north of town, testing our drugs. You can go take a look at him if you need to, but he's busy almost all the time... either with the drugs or with women.}
{Speech 16 Answer 7}{}{Myron? Alright, Jesus. Thanks for the talk.}
